texts.content: {"text":"23. Bas, Biz qodir bo`ldik va qandoq ham yaxshi qodir bo`luvchimiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,67]}]}

{"text":"27. Va Biz unda yuksak tog`lar qildik \nva sizlarni zilol suv bilan sug`ordik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,77]}]}

{"text":"31. U, salqin qiluvchimas va olovni ham qaytarmas.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,50]}]}

{"text":"38. Bu ajratish kuni sizlarni va avvalgilarni jamladik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,55]}]}

{"text":"43. Yenglar va ichinglar, osh bo`lsin. \nQilgan amallaringiz sababidandir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,73]}]}

{"text":"46. Yenglar va mazza qilinglar, ozginagina. \nAlbatta, sizlar gunohkorsizlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,76]}]}

{"text":"48. Va agar ularga ruku' qilinglar deyilsa, \nruku' qilmaslar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,61]}]}
